  "notes": "Test-only NVFP4 sibling derived from the official Ideogram4 workflow. It defaults to the official Quality sampler preset, preserves the app-standard size controls and CFGOverride flow, supports the Ideogram4 layout canvas JSON caption path, and shares the backend canvas repair that fuses object modules while keeping text modules precisely positioned with invisible bbox placement. It routes DualModelGuider model_negative to the same main model branch instead of the separate unconditional UNET so false-positive/noise behavior can be compared against the official baseline."
